tyle: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> loose terminology</a> that we have b=
een using recently, a crypto bank:=C2=A0It takes money (cryptocurrency, sta=
blecoins, etc.) from =E2=80=9Cdepositors=E2=80=9D (customers) and lends mon=
